    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The most problem of all PDF creators is i18n. For arabic and persian languages we need two feature.
* Right to left (<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Right-to-left">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Right-to-left</a>)
** "سلام بر شما ای دوستان." {color:red}Dot character must be the left position of sentence. This page is Left to right also in PDF.{color} 
* Joined characters
** "سلام" {color:green}correct{color} 
** "س‌ل‌ا‌م" {color:red}wrong{color}</p>

<p>This two may help Zend i18n more feature. Thanks.
Useful : <a href="http://www.tcpdf.org/">http://www.tcpdf.org/</a>
Persian and Arabic language on RTL document in TCPDF:
<a href="http://www.tcpdf.org/examples/example_018.pdf">http://www.tcpdf.org/examples/example_018.pdf</a></p>

